SUMMARY:Rock the Park
LOCATION:600 N Ashley Dr Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Rock the Park is a FREE monthly music series showcasing musica
 l talents of all genres. Rock the Park is typically held at Tampas Curtis 
 Hixon Waterfront Park on the first Thursday of each month and facilitated 
 through a 15 year partnership between the Tampa Downtown Partnership Broke
 nmold Entertainment. Upcoming Dates: February 5\, 2026 at 6pm: EMO NIGHT!!
