LOCATION:1701 N Highland Ave Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:The 13th Annual Walk for Wishes Tampa will take place on Satur
 day\, April 11\, 2026. Lace up your shoes and join us for a heartwarming d
 ay of fitness and fun at Water Works Park! For additional event details\, 
 please visit walkforwishestampa.org. Walk For Wishes is a feel-good event 
