SUMMARY:Earth Day Celebration
LOCATION:110 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:In the spirit of celebrating Mother Earth\, join us this Satur
 day\, April 18! From 9:30am to 3pm\, well have special guests\, animal fri
 ends\, and experts sharing how we can all take care of our planet. The cel
 ebration continues in our MakeSpace exhibit! Throughout April and May\, fa
 milies can explore eco-friendly art by transforming recycled materials int
 o creative masterpieces that celebrate our planet! Sponsored by The Ball F
 oundation. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/188931
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/188931
