SUMMARY:Rock the Cosmos: Prince- Laser Light Show in Planetarium
LOCATION:4801 E Fowler Ave. Tampa \, FL 33617 United States
DESCRIPTION:Experience the intersection of music\, science\, and art at th
 e Museum of Science Innovation (MOSI). Held in the Holloway Digital Dome T
 heatrehome to the Saunders Planetariumthese shows feature vivid laser visu
 als and dynamic special effects set to legendary soundtracks. Event Highli
 ghts Immersive Atmosphere: Step inside Americas second-largest planetarium
  for a 360-degree sensory experience. Live Star Show: Every performance be
 gins with a 10-minute guided tour of the night sky led by a MOSI astronome
 r. Diverse Music Themes: Rotating monthly shows ranging from Taylor Swift 
 and Prince to Pink Floyd\, Metallica\, and seasonal holiday specials. On-S
 ite Amenities: Beakers Bar opens at 5:30 PM for pre-show drinks and refres
 hments. Quick Details When: Select Friday evenings. Showtimes: 6:30 PM and
  8:15 PM. Location: 4801 E. Fowler Avenue\, Tampa\, FL. Cost: 10 for Membe
 rs  13 for Non-Members. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/189036
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189036
