SUMMARY:Charity Casino Night
LOCATION:522 N Howard Ave Tampa \, FL 33606 United States
DESCRIPTION:Are you looking for a night of excitement that also supports h
 undreds of hospice patients across Hillsborough\, Pinellas\, and Pasco cou
 nties? Mark your calendars! Gulfside Hospice will host its Sixth Annual Ch
 arity Casino Night on Friday\, April 24\, at the Shanna and Bryan Glazer J
 CC in Tampa. This one-of-a-kind event directly supports hospice patients t
 hrough donations and sponsorships\, all while offering thrilling casino st
 yle games such as Blackjack\, Roulette\, Texas Hold Em\, Poker\, slot mach
 ines\, and more. Guests will be immersed in a lively casino atmosphere com
 plete with card tables\, roulette wheels\, delicious bites\, adult beverag
 es\, and a fun photo booth. Whether youre a seasoned poker player or a fir
 st time guest trying your luck\, the evening promises something for everyo
 ne. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187416
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/187416
END:VEVENT
