SUMMARY:Ink Mania Fest
LOCATION:4800 US-301 S\, Tampa\, FL 33610 Tampa \, FL 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:Ink Mania Fest is a threeday\, highenergy celebration of tatto
 o culture\, art\, music\, and communityuniting thousands of artists\, enth
 usiasts\, families\, and creators under one roof at the Florida State Fair
 grounds in Tampa\, Florida . This festival blends worldclass tattooing wit
 h live entertainment\, interactive experiences\, and nonstop action\, maki
 ng it one of Floridas most dynamic and inclusive art events.  Event Dates 
 Hours Friday\, April 24 12:00 PM  11:00 PM Opening day kicks off with live
  tattooing\, vendors\, music\, and the first round of competitions. Saturd
 ay\, April 25 11:00 AM  11:00 PM Our biggest daypacked with MMA fights\, p
 erformances\, food trucks\, and fullday tattoo showcases. Sunday\, April 2
 6 11:00 AM  8:00 PM Final competitions\, awards\, family activities\, and 
 lastchance tattoo sessions.  Festival Highlights  Live MMA Fights Highinte
 nsity MMA bouts bring adrenaline and excitement to the festival floor. Fig
 hters from across the region compete in a professional\, actionpacked show
 case that keeps the crowd on its feet.  Graffiti Wall Live Art Watch artis
 ts transform massive walls into vibrant murals in real time. The graffiti 
 zone is a fan favoritecolorful\, bold\, and perfect for photos.  Live Tatt
 ooing Hundreds of elite tattoo artists from around the world tattoo live a
 ll weekend. Attendees can book appointments\, walk up for flash\, or simpl
 y watch the artistry unfold.  Tattoo Competitions Daily competitions highl
 ight the best of the bestblack grey\, color\, realism\, traditional\, port
 rait\, and more. Sundays Best of Show crowns the top artist of the weekend
 .  Music Entertainment Live DJs\, performers\, and special guests bring no
 nstop energy to the main stage. From hiphop to rock to cultural showcases\
 , the entertainment lineup keeps the vibe electric.  Food Truck Village A 
 curated selection of food trucks offers everything from gourmet street foo
 d to sweet treats. Perfect for families\, artists\, and hungry festivalgoe
 rs. Unique vendors fill the expo with art\, jewelry\, clothing\, tattoo su
 pplies\, collectibles\, and handcrafted goods.  FamilyFriendly Experience 
 Ink Mania Fest welcomes all ages. With art zones\, safe walkways\, food op
 tions\, and a positive community atmosphere\, families can enjoy the festi
 val together.  Community Culture Ink Mania Fest celebrates creativity\, di
 versity\, and unity. Its more than a tattoo conventionits a cultural exper
 ience where artists\, supporters\, and families come together to share pas
 sion and expression. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187276
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/187276
END:VEVENT
