DESCRIPTION:Tampa Family Health Centers (TFHC) hosts an interactive class 
 about how to prepare for hurricane season. Visit our vendor displays to le
 arn about available resources so you can make a plan. Each participant wil
 l receive free hurricane preparedness materials. Visit our WellFed table f
 rom 11:00 AM - 12:00 PM and taste samples of easy and delicious recipes. R
 egistration: This is a free class. TFHC will provide the materials\, but r
 egistration is required. Please note: Call or email Nicole Pinson\, npinso
 nhcnetwork.org or 813-459-3831\, TFHC Garden Manager\, with questions. Spa
 ce is limited to 50 participants. Event Location: The class begins at 9:30
  AM. We will be located in the Employee Breakroom. We have a water cooler 
