SUMMARY:Juneteenth 5K CommUnity WalkRun
LOCATION:7525 N Boulevard Tampa \, FL 33604 United States
DESCRIPTION:The Juneteenth 5K CommUnity WalkRun is a free\, family-friendl
 y event that brings the Tampa community together to celebrate culture\, mo
 vement\, and health. Hosted by Smart Health Initiatives\, this unique even
 t blends the spirit of Juneteenth with a focus on preventing type 2 diabet
 es through accessible wellness activities. Participants of all fitness lev
 els are encouraged to walk or run the 5K course while engaging in a broade
 r community experience that includes a Health Wellness Village\, free heal
 th screenings\, educational resources\, music\, and community partner acti
 vations. This event is part of the Healthy Soles Endurance Series\, suppor
 ting initiatives like Fit Futures\, a youth program that promotes healthy 
 habits through running and nutrition education. \n\nPermalink: https://www
 .tampa.gov/node/188861
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/188861
END:VEVENT
